headline: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. Acquires First Actuarial
summary: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. today announced the acquisition of UK-based First Actuarial. Terms of the transaction were not disclosed.

headline: Is Arthur J. Gallagher Stock Underperforming the S&P 500?
summary: Arthur J. Gallagher has significantly underperformed the S&P 500 over the past year, yet analysts remain bullish on the stock’s prospects.
